{"tid":1122880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想問各位大隻佬睇咩大？","createTime":"2019-04-24T07:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:23:58.000Z","uid":203864,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf94c9b921b04f97e70df22c861c88c63f8a34ef","tid":1122880,"uid":203864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"小弟最近有開始想認真操下 玩下健身 <br />\n其實我就好耐之前已經有睇開啲唔同嘅Youtuber 去獲取更多相關資訊 <br />\n例如： 飲食、健身姿勢、熱身動作同埋如何去保護自己既肌肉同埋各類supplement <br />\n小弟大約係5-6年前左右就開始睇 Mike Chang （sixpack shortcut) 佢可以話係我既啟蒙老師！ <br />\n由係YouTube無意間睇到佢條廣告既時候就開始follow 直到佢離開個channel <br />\n佢都比咗好多健身資訊比我<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nE4TbrE0VkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnE4TbrE0VkU&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=fe3a8326\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nE4TbrE0VkU</a><br />\n就係呢條片令我對健身起興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而另一個我好鍾意睇既Youtube Chanel <br />\nATHLEAN-X (Jeff )<br />\n呢個就偏向於學術性既資訊 當然也有教大家點操 點練 先會達到更好既效果 <br />\n當我拉傷 整親 我都會睇呢個channel去睇下 點樣去紓緩痛楚 點樣去拉返筋 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=80&amp;v=zyvjscQVFv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D80%26v%3DzyvjscQVFv8&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=0f7cb708\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=80&amp;v=zyvjscQVFv8</a><br />\n<br />\n而最最最近睇既Youtube channel <br />\n反而係大陸既Youtuber 健助師小珂 其實佢同Jeff既channel都好相同 <br />\n但呢個主要語言係用中文去拍攝（小弟英文唔係咁好） 好多時用翻中文去聽 會令我更容易去理解 去明白點解要做呢個動作、點解要咁樣去減脂等等。 （如果要插請細力小小）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OjYRdCIFLHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOjYRdCIFLHI&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=c08cfceb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OjYRdCIFLHI</a><br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得既係要支持翻我地本地既YouTube channel Kofgym <br />\n由呢個channel出世我就開始睇 由最初幾百 幾千view 睇到而家萬幾 幾萬view 我都好開心睇到 香港健身 都開始慢慢多人了解 更願意去接觸健身資訊！ <br />\n由最初初搞笑 翻譯翻外國大隻佬既健身片 到而家更多學術片 同香港健身 健美既大隻佬合作 拍片 讓大家認識更多香港健身！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TVddFj_7Lc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTVddFj_7Lc8&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=f6c0980c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TVddFj_7Lc8</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知各位連登健美先生 又係睇咩channel大 又係點樣開始接觸健身呢？ 期待你地無私既分享"},{"pid":"f7451a49cbb802f7fbba3274dab4886a5df3568b","tid":1122880,"uid":78971,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"我哋連登仔念力健身<br />\n想邊度大，邊度就大"},{"pid":"6d6fefb067a2389c8306ddbde86bdc87acf171fb","tid":1122880,"uid":39157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇 連登仔一下掌上壓就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cfcde3951a780a7040bcc2f83c9dc88315082e","tid":1122880,"uid":203864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"推推推！"},{"pid":"3bb105982d33eae95bb87d941da4791644e466e6","tid":1122880,"uid":203864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"9717805cc12048488c6b9bea287a9397d085365f","tid":1122880,"uid":123156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"我睇放學ICU大 細細就開始睇 睇到佢完"},{"pid":"d0d2204b0e96dfd7a3777e0e7c23b6e77db3fb5c","tid":1122880,"uid":203864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9717805cc12048488c6b9bea287a9397d085365f","tid":1122880,"uid":123156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"我睇放學ICU大 細細就開始睇 睇到佢完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"呢位師兄講野咁風趣 實溝死女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed74cfe012ca43c7c8970ecb08522f811ee6f59e","tid":1122880,"u